  "title": "Mechanical & Electrical Engineer | Maritime | Vessel Engine System | Training Provided",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Maritime Transportation Industry . Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Marine Electrical Engineer to be part of their Team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the West - easily accessible.</strong><br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and design control systems in accordance with project specifications.</li><li>Prepare technical drawings for customer review and approval.</li><li>Generate detailed drawings and Bill of Materials (BOM/BCM) for shop floor production.</li><li>Coordinate with clients, consultants, and internal departments to ensure smooth project execution.</li><li>Perform drafting tasks using CAD software, including AutoCAD and SolidWorks.</li><li>Carry out any other ad-hoc duties as assigned to support project needs.\\</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree in Electrical Engineering.</li><li>Hands on experience with vessel mechanical and engine systems.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.<br />We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</p><p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.<br />EA License No: 19C9682<br />EA Personnel No: R25157233 (Loh Pooi Keng)</p>",
